downloadTitle: Change Management and TFS Integration for Multi-Developer Projects White paper
downloadDescription: This document describes development tasks and best practices that are related to application life cycle management in Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012. It focuses on managing metadata changes across Microsoft Dynamics AX installations when multiple developers are working on the same application.
